==English==
===Noun===
(''grammatical terminology''): noun [[case]] used to indicate [[adjacent]] location. In English, this is usually expressed by the prepositions '''near''', '''at''', or '''by''', as in "by the house." Languages that use the adessive case include [[Finnish]], [[Hungarian]], [[Estonian]], and [[Lithuanian]].

